msgid "What to do?"
msgstr "要做什么呢？"

msgid "Kill it here"
msgstr "把它杀死"

msgid "Release it around this area"
msgstr "把它放到周围去"

msgid "Do nothing"
msgstr "什么也不做"

msgid "It's not wise to do that here."
msgstr "在这里这么做并不明智。"

msgid "I don't think I should release it so close to them..."
msgstr "我觉得我不应该在离它们这么近的地方就把它放生掉..."

msgid "HEY! I'M WATCHING YOU!"
msgstr "嘿！我们在看着你呢！"

msgid "IF YOU LET THAT SHIT FREE I'LL COME OUT AND KILL YOU BOTH MYSELF!!!"
msgstr "如果你把那傻逼东西放走，我就出来亲手杀了你们俩！！！"

msgid "(...Sorry...)"
msgstr "（...对不起...）"

msgid "A rudimentary lamp."
msgstr "一盏简陋的灯。"

msgid "A tent. Looks rather cozy."
msgstr "帐篷。看起来相当舒适。"

msgid "There's nothing particularly interesting about the backside of the tent."
msgstr "帐篷的背面没什么特别有趣的地方。"

msgid "Stay away!!!"
msgstr "别过来！！！"
